# FresKoExpress — Angular 21 Frontend

## Stack
- Angular 21, zoneless, Signal Forms, standalone components
- Angular Material + SCSS
- All state: Angular Signals only
- All forms: Signal Forms only (no FormBuilder, no FormGroup)
- No RxJS for state management
- Base API URL: http://localhost:8080

## Context handoff rules
- When context usage exceeds 50%, finish the current file completely
- Then propose new_task with:
  * Files completed so far
  * Next pending task
  * Stack constraints above
  * Any decisions made (interfaces, folder structure)

## Folder structure to maintain
src/app/
  core/          (interceptors, guards, auth service)
  shared/        (components, pipes, models)
  features/
    auth/
    proveedores/
    inventario/
    pedidos/
    rutas/
    facturacion/
    sensores/
    mantenimiento/
    dashboard/